title: Prime location! Amazing floorplans at Stoneleigh at the Reserve
posting_body: ['Stoneleigh at the Reserve', 'Visit Our Community Today!', '5200 Annapolis Ln N', 'Plymouth, MN 55446', 'show contact info', "The only thing that rivals Stoneleigh's exceptional property is our premium location that's just 15 miles northwest of Minneapolis.", "Here you'll have easy access to I-494, and a public bus stop is just steps outside our front door.", "The Reserve Park is a five-minute walk down the street: it's a great place to have a picnic, go for a walk, or let the kids run and play.", "Just down the road, you'll find Rockford Road Plaza where you can pick up necessities at Target, grab a quick burger at Five Guys, and discover the latest fashions at Kohl's.", 'Bedrooms: 2 |  Bathrooms:  2', 'Square Footage: 1376 sq ft', 'Rental Pricing: $2175/Month', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '● Bike Storage', '● Car Wash Bay', '● Coffee Station', '● Conference Room', '● Elevator', '● Fitness Center', '● Free Weights', '● Gameroom', '● Picnic Area', '● Recycling', '● Barbecue/Grill Area', '● Basketball Half-Court', '● Business Center', '● Cardio Machines', '● Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '● Controlled Access Building', '● Disposal Chutes', '● On-site Maintenance & Management', '● Planned Social Activities', '● Reserveable Clubhouse', 'This Unit Comes With:', '● Air Conditioning', '● Built-In Office/Desk', 'In Select Units', '● Ceiling Fans In Select Units', '● Dining Room', '● Dishwasher', '● Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '● Garbage Disposal', '● Microwave', '● Pantry In Select Units', '● Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Phone-Number:', 'show contact info', 'Pet-Policy: Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'Lease-Length: Variable', 'Call for Directions', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'A4A7024A9456404']
